title: IAA Tonight | Christian McCaffrey Completes TD Trifecta AND Michigan vs. Michigan St. Tunnel Brawl
description: The addition of Christian McCaffrey is paying off immensely for the San Francisco 49ers. The All-Pro running back scored three touchdowns on Sunday by rushing, passing and receiving. Would a fully healthy 49ers squad possibly be able to beat the undefeated Eagles in the NFC? Pacman Jones, Antoine Walker and Leger Douzable discuss that and the tunnel brawl that happened after Michigan def. Michigan St. in Ann Arbor on Saturday. One hosts believes that it would be ridiculous for charges to be filed.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Leger Douzable, Adam Pacman Jones, Antoine Walker)
